# X11

new_client x x11
create x/1 csd
show x/1

move x/1 100 100
assert_position x/1 100 100

maximize x/1
wait_reconfigure
assert_position x/1 0 0

unmaximize x/1
wait_reconfigure
assert_position x/1 100 100

tile x/1 left
wait_reconfigure
assert_position x/1 0 0

untile x/1
wait_reconfigure
